					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Thao Thai</h4>
												<button class="fa fa-link"></button>
												<p>Thao is the author of <em>Banyan Moon</em>, the July 2023 Read with Jenna title, Barnes & Noble Discover Pick, and Book of the Month selection. <em>Banyan Moon</em> was also selected by booksellers as an IndieNext pick and longlisted for the Center for Fiction's First Novel Prize. A recipient of the 2024 Ohio Arts Council’s Individual Excellence Award, her work has been published in the <em>Los Angeles Review of Books</em>, <em>WIRED</em>, <em>Elle</em>, <em>Lit Hub</em>, and other publications. She lives in central Ohio with her husband and daughter.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			
